Package: rand36sf
Type: Package
Title: Recode and score the RAND 36-SF Health Survey
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Eslam", "Maher",
      email = "e.maher@imperial.ac.uk"
    ),
    person(
      "Aya", "Khalil",
      email = "a.khalil@imperial.ac.uk"
    )
  )
Description: This function recodes and scores the eight scales of the RAND SF-36
  health survey from raw item responses in a dataframe. Items are recoded to
  a 0-100 scale and then averaged to create the 8 scales.
Imports: dplyr, purrr
